  "1745210": {
    "name": "Timewell: Trail of Celestes",
    "steam_appid": 1745210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/dadfb48057f75df0065c968a374a4733.avif?t=1685965181\" width=670 height=160 /></span><br><br><strong>Timewell: Trail of Celestes</strong> combines the excitement of a <strong>space shooter</strong> with the depth of a <strong>story-driven RPG</strong>. As the A.I. SAT-V, pilot a Vulcan class space fighter through the Timewell Universe using 4 DOF (4 degree of freedom) gameplay. SAT-V has a unique artificial personality and can adapt to different levels of difficulty by changing its capabilities through skills and adaptations, on the fly. Use your strategy and skill points to guide SAT-V to victory in this fast-paced space combat adventure.<br><br>* Note: Trailer and Game Music Credits go to most talented composer and music scientist Scott Buckley. You certainly rock my friend ! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/87446d12ee4e6128200b4d2164498b3f.poster.avif?t=1685965181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/87446d12ee4e6128200b4d2164498b3f.webm?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/87446d12ee4e6128200b4d2164498b3f.mp4?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/445f67af3c8b1605b6215d08c9f05e94.avif?t=1685965181\" width=670 height=160 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Timewell Universe:</strong> Trail of Celestes is the first installment in Timewell Universe where <strong>Space Combat</strong> meets story-driven gameplay and <strong>Space RPG</strong>. Can you uncover the truth behind the struggle of supreme beings known as Celestes and their formidable opponents, Constructs?</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/cc28cb68fe479467340ca5d9af179f5b.poster.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/cc28cb68fe479467340ca5d9af179f5b.webm?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/cc28cb68fe479467340ca5d9af179f5b.mp4?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Story Mode:</strong> A tale of suspense and deceit takes place in the exotic corners of the galaxy. You control a Vulcan class space fighter as the A.I. SAT-V. Can you guide her to her destiny on this RPG themed space shooter? </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/d8e6fb63b2f2003483838e0c61f4d2ae.poster.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/d8e6fb63b2f2003483838e0c61f4d2ae.webm?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/d8e6fb63b2f2003483838e0c61f4d2ae.mp4?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Skills / Adaptations:</strong> Having an artificial personality of its own, SAT-V can adapt to varying degrees of difficulties and change its capabilities via skills and adaptations. You can alter the skill points and perks on the fly and enhance your gameplay with different tactics. Can you overcome perils with brain as well as brawn?</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/e72c232776dcea3210162fd6c782de65.poster.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/e72c232776dcea3210162fd6c782de65.webm?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/e72c232776dcea3210162fd6c782de65.mp4?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Achievements / Relics:</strong> Fun feats that can be unlocked throughout the game provide Relics as rewards and they are added to your inventory on each play through. These relics are alien artifacts that can boost SAT-V’s stats and skills. Once unlocked via Achievements, Epic and Legendary Relics provide unique boosts to your gaming style.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/d32c7d3f7430ec88e7b5c0beaec1b012.poster.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/d32c7d3f7430ec88e7b5c0beaec1b012.webm?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/d32c7d3f7430ec88e7b5c0beaec1b012.mp4?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Customize Looks:</strong> You can customize look and feel of your ship with paint modes randomly looted from enemies. When unlocked, they are yours and you can use them on each play through.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/066277b3439571d027079527a75c10e4.poster.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/066277b3439571d027079527a75c10e4.webm?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/066277b3439571d027079527a75c10e4.mp4?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Skirmish Mode:</strong> For casual players, fast skirmish mode with different world settings is also included. Each zone has a secret mini-boss to encounter. Are you up for the challenge for this <strong>space combat RPG</strong>? </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/5be4982ccff33c7bb1599d0fd5ed0288.poster.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/5be4982ccff33c7bb1599d0fd5ed0288.webm?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/5be4982ccff33c7bb1599d0fd5ed0288.mp4?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Easter Eggs:</strong> Funny (and somewhat mysterious?!) easter eggs wait for you to be discovered. Can you solve the riddles of The Unfathomable Scholar ? Can you ?!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/73b106339910768fe265b8938cfff7ba.poster.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/73b106339910768fe265b8938cfff7ba.webm?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/73b106339910768fe265b8938cfff7ba.mp4?t=1685965181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Enjoy and breath in the rich atmosphere of Timewell Universe where SAT-V plays a key role in the survival of three galactic races. May you guide SAT-V to her destination through an adventure of deceit and suspense?<br><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Story</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/0de6a071295c9ca63709843788ded526.avif?t=1685965181\" width=670 height=160 /></span><br><br><strong>In the year 3099, earth had a major crisis of resources, pollution, and unjust economy. Governments controlled by megatechs invested in creating the ultimate artificial intelligence with a personality to increase their reach in the galaxy.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/9882a4cf73835cbd7eb8a263e132f1d8.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>SAT-V (Super Adaptive Tech), the latest version of artificial intelligence research was designed to overcome perils with unparalleled ingenuity as well as firepower.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/c899a1131180ba91313f29029c53bd1e.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><strong>Burdened with the task of finding a goldilocks planet of bountiful resources, SAT-V got a mysterious signal of an unknown origin on the outskirts of Titan.</strong><br><br>Reaching the destination, SAT-V encountered a portal, a gaping hole in the fabric of spacetime. Without hesitation, it took the first step in the human history and made the perilous jump.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/5ee8e74b5659d1564ab4ca03b68f2d3d.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><strong>After the spacetime jump, SAT-V had a startling revelation: an unknown entity emerged from SAT-V’s cerebral nexus and took the leading role of her virtual personalities. Providing little information about its origin, the entity gave SAT-V various tasks to reach the final destination, where humanity will be rewarded by supreme beings mentioned as Celestes.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/29f026ac496acca561c8610ec4bcb98e.avif?t=1685965181\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><i>Thus starts the Trail Of Celestes…</i><br><br><strong>See you folks in the next cycle where the story continues ! :)</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745210/extras/d7f5a010a6fc035c86945e0b8364c4dc.avif?t=1685965181\" width=670 height=160 /></span>",
